Widget.Name: e_st_SlideShowTips
Widget.Text:
Slideshow Tips
1) Press and hold to remain on the current image
2) Do not remove the SD card while the image is loading
3) Tap to skip to the next image

Widget.Text:
Demonstrated Features
WQVGA display Integrated MTCH6301 PCAP touch input Low-Cost Controller-less Graphics driver Real-time JPEG, BMP, GIF decoding Transparent GIF support Images retrieved from SD card Up to 16-bit color depth support
